title: Toxic Storm 01 (of 04) (2013) (Digital) (K6-Empire) (- Nem -)
description: Welcome to Raining Hills Asylum. Home to the damned and unwanted ranks of the criminally insane. Patient X recounts his story to Doctor Susan Parsons during a psychological review. His tale is one full of betrayal, murder and black magic. A twist of fate presents Patient X a chance of freedom and escape. Stand witness to the origin and birth of one of the most original and talked about characters from recent independent comics in this supernatural thriller. Read the book that Comicbooked called "An amazing comic series".
